  "2257110": {
    "name": "STACK & the Grumblepuff from Above",
    "steam_appid": 2257110,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play as Stack – a tower of buddies just trying to take a nap – when mysterious grumbles start falling from the sky! Dodge them, weave them, and swerve to grab some coins. Develop a healthy addiction to coins as you find the source of your sleeping debacle… from above. Maybe grab a friend (or seven) along the way.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are many ways to play, the game supports WASD, arrow keys, controller, mouse and touchscreen. There’s also a range of options to tweak so that the game can run more smoothly on different devices.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Players without fast reaction time can also benefit from the assist modes, that allow you to play the regular game, but without any finicky button inputs.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can also play with between 2 and 7 other players for local co-op or party modes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257110/extras/de91b500f7fdb924d8f7c39763f30f16.webp?t=1756465022\" width=640 height=42 /></span>Play through eight different levels as you find the source of these mysterious falling grumbles. Each level has a unique gimmick which will change up how you must approach it. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257110/extras/252ce1a480047c0b59c124d7ca1c5126.poster.avif?t=1756465022\" width=700 height=290 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257110/extras/252ce1a480047c0b59c124d7ca1c5126.webm?t=1756465022\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257110/extras/252ce1a480047c0b59c124d7ca1c5126.mp4?t=1756465022\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257110/extras/edebfa1480cba34583ae2b6012a61f43.webp?t=1756465022\" width=640 height=42 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play with a buddy and work through the story mode together or play locally with up to seven friends to battle it out for a victor! There are 7 unique powerups to fight with. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257110/extras/cd74a3add1a02655b8265b42a5c6f7ce.poster.avif?t=1756465022\" width=700 height=290 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257110/extras/cd74a3add1a02655b8265b42a5c6f7ce.webm?t=1756465022\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257110/extras/cd74a3add1a02655b8265b42a5c6f7ce.mp4?t=1756465022\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257110/extras/51a5f5720cdaf40f612085a4ddfab132.webp?t=1756465022\" width=640 height=42 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Got a spare minute? Rounds are fast and can be played for short periods. And between the achievements, coin goals and high scores, you’ll be kept busy!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257110/extras/6dab4c215c32c7d70ee1259e7cc7a465.poster.avif?t=1756465022\" width=700 height=290 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257110/extras/6dab4c215c32c7d70ee1259e7cc7a465.webm?t=1756465022\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257110/extras/6dab4c215c32c7d70ee1259e7cc7a465.mp4?t=1756465022\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257110/extras/3a43fc281589ca1462d52365995ab221.webp?t=1756465022\" width=640 height=42 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Change settings in MENU&gt;OPTIONS, including audio, visual, system and accessibility options. There are also Settings Presets to quickly make adjustments.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257110/extras/d4f080a9273aec5c810327e985050c16.poster.avif?t=1756465022\" width=700 height=290 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257110/extras/d4f080a9273aec5c810327e985050c16.webm?t=1756465022\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257110/extras/d4f080a9273aec5c810327e985050c16.mp4?t=1756465022\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257110/extras/d8e8c72e9ce481b7aa1028c6e29add1d.webp?t=1756465022\" width=640 height=42 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Program and modify the game with Datapackles. Perform commands in the in-game console, and create Datapackles which have functionality for custom levels, and other shenanigans. See the documentation to learn more.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257110/extras/9e1b0de86521ee071f81a6268ca5254e.avif?t=1756465022\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257110/extras/25e699153dfc0331bb85577d39fe445c.webp?t=1756465022\" width=640 height=42 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Updates to <i>STACK &amp; the Gumblepuff from Above</i>. See MENU&gt;INFO in-game for a complete summary.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >1.13.2 July 2025</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >1.13.1 May 2025</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >1.13 April 2024 // Quality of Life Update</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >1.12.1  January 2025 // New Music</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >1.12 December 2024 // Multiplayer</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >1.11.1 November 2024 // Datapackles</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >1.11 October 2024 // Story Update</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >1.10.4 September 2024 // The Grumblepuff, Atmosphere &amp; Bugs Update</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >1.10.3.1 August 2024 // Initial Cutscene Bug</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >1.10.3 August 2024 // Later Levels &amp; Bugs Update</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >1.10.2 June 2024 // Massive Performance Improvements &amp; Updated Animations Update</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >1.10.1 April 2024 // Story Mode Improvements Update</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >1.10.0 February 2024 // Story Mode Update</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >1.9.1 January 2024 // Fonts Update</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >1.9.0 December 2023 // Initial Story Mode Update </h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >1.8.2 July 2023 // Bug Fixes</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >1.8.0 July 2023 // Miscellaneous Update</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >1.7.2 April 2023 // Bug Fixes</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >1.7.1 January 2023 // Critical Save File Bug Fix</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >1.7.0 January 2023 // Bug Fixes Update</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >1.6.0 November 2022 // GUI &amp; Bug Fixes Update</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >1.4.0 July 2022 // Achievements, PVP &amp; Hats Update</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >1.3.0 April 2022 // Trails and Game Modes Update</h2>",
